{"id":467,"ayahs":[{"number":75,"arabic":"وَتَرَى ٱلْمَلَٰٓئِكَةَ حَآفِّينَ مِنْ حَوْلِ ٱلْعَرْشِ يُسَبِّحُونَ بِحَمْدِ رَبِّهِمْ ۖ وَقُضِىَ بَيْنَهُم بِٱلْحَقِّ وَقِيلَ ٱلْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ رَبِّ ٱلْعَٰلَمِينَ","translation":"And thou wilt see the angels surrounding the throne of [God’s] almightiness, extolling their Sus­tainer’s glory and praise. And judgment will have been passed in justice on all [who had lived and died], and the word will be spoken: “All praise is due to God, the Sustainer of all the worlds!”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4133.mp3","surahId":39,"words":[{"id":62148,"position":1,"arabic":"وَتَرَى","translation":"এবং দেখবে তুমি","audioUrl":"wbw/039_075_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62149,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْمَلَـٰٓئِكَةَ","translation":"ফেরেশতাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_075_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62150,"position":3,"arabic":"حَآفِّينَ","translation":"ঘিরে থাকতে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_075_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62151,"position":4,"arabic":"مِنْ","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_075_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62152,"position":5,"arabic":"حَوْلِ","translation":"পাশ","audioUrl":"wbw/039_075_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62153,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْعَرْشِ","translation":"আরশের","audioUrl":"wbw/039_075_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62154,"position":7,"arabic":"يُسَبِّحُونَ","translation":"তারা মহিমা ঘোষণা করতে থাকবে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_075_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62155,"position":8,"arabic":"بِحَمْدِ","translation":"প্রশংসাসহ","audioUrl":"wbw/039_075_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62156,"position":9,"arabic":"رَبِّهِمْ ۖ","translation":"তাদের রবের","audioUrl":"wbw/039_075_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62158,"position":10,"arabic":"وَقُضِىَ","translation":"এবং বিচার করে দেওয়া হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/039_075_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62159,"position":11,"arabic":"بَيْنَهُم","translation":"তাদের মাঝে","